{{nihongo| '''Okuani Station'''|<U+5965><U+963F><U+4EC1><U+99C5>|Okuani-eki}} is a railway station located in [[Kitaakita, Akita|Kitaakita]], [[Akita Prefecture]], [[Japan]].

==Lines==
Okuani Station is served by the [[Akita Nairiku J<U+016B>kan Railway Akita Nairiku Line]], and is located 49.7 km from the terminus of the line at [[Takanosu Station]]. 

==Station layout==
Okuani Station consists of a single [[side platform]] serving bi-directional traffic. The station is unattended.  

